STARTUP
=======

Usage
     Name of an ARexx script which will be executed every time Most
     opens a window.  (see @{"ARexx Port" Link "ARexx Port"}).

     Remember that you can use directly all ARexx commands as tooltypes
     in project icons of text files (as a sort of "tooltype script").


@EndNode

