Keyboard commands
*****************

   In the current version Most supports all (and more!) keyboard
shortcuts well known from More. Future versions will allow custom
keyboard commands...


 @{" Scrolling " Link "Scrolling"} 
 @{" Searching " Link "Searching"} 
 @{" Open file " Link "Open file"} 
 @{" Edit file " Link "Edit file"} 
 @{" Info requester " Link "Info requester"} 
