Searching
=========

search actual searchstring again
     @{b}n@{ub}

ignore upper/lower case
     @{b}.@{ub}

searching with distinction of upper/lower case
     @{b}/@{ub}

Open the search requester
     @{b}f@{ub} @{b}s@{ub}


@EndNode

@Node "Open file" "Most_engl.guide/Open file"
@Next "Info requester"
