Template
     Open @{b}FILE/K@{ub}

Usage
     Load a new text in the current window. The filename is optional.
     If you don't specify a name a filerequester opens.  This command
     doesn't return until the window is closed again!

Example
             Open @{b}FILE@{ub} Most.dok


