Known bugs
**********

   -     Several control sequences for cursor movements trash the
     display.

   -     Most has problems with the pipe of WShell.

   - An Enforcer-hit with Most 1.53 has been reported which may be still
     there. The input buffer seems to overflow after havy input...

   - Bruno Lacombe reported a Mungwall hit with Most 1.53 I couldn't
     reproduce here...


@EndNode

