(132.231.1.10) in the directory  @{b}pub/amiga/local/UweR@{ub}. You will also
find other interesting software in @{b}pub/amiga/local@{ub} ...

   I try to upload new releases of Most on AmiNet and on our local BBS
"Die Box Passau" (2:2494/22.0) as soon as possible.


